data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Rio Rico! This charming single-family gem boasts 3 beds, 2 baths, and a spacious 2-car garage. But that's not all - it comes with an additional detached 2-car garage, currently a finished, heated/cooled workspace, perfect for a home office or studio. Built in 2000, this beauty sits on a sprawling half-acre lot adorned with mature trees and breathtaking mountain views. At an elevation of approximately 4,000 feet above sea level, you'll enjoy the serenity of this unique Southwestern oasis. Don't miss this rare opportunity! Did I mention: the entire property is fenced, it's half an acre, has great views, it has fresh interior paint,  wraparound patio, one large covered north facing patio, and mature trees ! Not to be missed!
